## Step 4: Refine

If the user requests changes, revise the specific section. Re-present only the changed
section, not the full framework.

When refining the differentiator, apply the three-test filter again (true, relevant,
exclusive) before accepting any new claim.

When refining pitches, preserve the formula structure — only change the words, not the
sequence of moves.

Repeat until user approves.

